{"tid":350294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中港牌私家車逆線駛入東廊支路　撞電單車釀2傷","createTime":"2017-08-07T06:35:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-07T12:50:08.000Z","uid":53379,"like":5,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6994cf14b266c98c44b2e057d04f3f6cbfacf5e5","tid":350294,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:35:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">私家車逆線駛入東廊支路　撞電單車釀2傷</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170807/s00001/4e531c95b69d9627693d31f20d9232be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170807%2Fs00001%2F4e531c95b69d9627693d31f20d9232be.jpg&h=d5639e3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n東區走廊發生車禍。早上10時許，一輛掛有中港車牌的私家車沿東區走廊西行，駛至太古城對開時，逆線駛入東區走廊東行支線，與一輛電單車迎頭相撞，電單車司機及乘客墮地受傷，清醒送院治理。私家車司機在場協助警方調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170807/s00001/1502081511712\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170807%2Fs00001%2F1502081511712&d=IzYqItrksY8bkNbUn20Pjcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=3a7c1338\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170807%2Fs00001%2F1502081511712&h=2ffcb400\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170807/s00001/1502081511712</a>"},{"pid":"2f2367822e31ab0de1b62d384ae3f6560746bd90","tid":350294,"uid":3342,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:36:19.000Z","msg":"屌成個車頭都係血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcbd222531d9b0403524ad3c915813a8032ee007","tid":350294,"uid":116289,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:37:14.000Z","msg":"支那蝗累人累物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/f